COMMUNITY GUIDELINES

We are building Dome Pro as a community project. To participate:

1. BE RESPECTFUL: Treat all community members with respect
2. BE COLLABORATIVE: Work together to improve the Software
3. BE CONSTRUCTIVE: Provide helpful feedback and suggestions
4. GIVE BACK: Consider contributing improvements to the Official Repository
5. SHARE KNOWLEDGE: Help others learn and use the Software

